Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With high hopes, humans\Nleave Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...to begin a new life in\Nthe Space Colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But the United Earth Sphere\NAlliance gains military power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...and in the name of\NJustice and Peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...seizes control of one\Ncolony after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To counter the Alliance's\Ntyranny, rebel colonists...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...bring new arsenals\Nto the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...disguising them as\Nshooting stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:02:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Alliance headquarters\Ncatches on to this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Others are attacking OZ\Nfacilities besides just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish I could meet them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is New Edwards Base reporting\Nthe shuttle's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Including ground vehicles,\Na considerable number are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I shrewdly spread rumors\Nthat all top officers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...of OZ will be coming\Nto New Edwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At least the part about you\Nand I being there will be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you counting yourself\Nin as a decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Positioning is 100% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't need to\Nincrease it any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So Zechs is in Nairobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we use him for\Nsomething more significant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have as many OZ\Nsoldiers stationed in Nairobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're expecting a fierce\Nbattle there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,People will stop doubting and\Nwill be devoted to a new future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ leaders will assemble\Nat New Edwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa's disappeared again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but he did say that\Nhe'd be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That punk keeps wandering off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally I wouldn't hesitate\Nto fire someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's too good to\Nget rid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make him earn his\Npay when he gets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa, how come you\Nkeep disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Quatre suddenly\Ntook off to a resort on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Must've been tired of hanging\Naround with old farts like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Quatre's left\Nus behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...so he could go alone\Non some type of mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He was concerned about our\Nsafety, so he left us behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But that'll put Quatre\Nin danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't refuse his kind\Nconsideration for our safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But Master Quatre, I wish\Nyou'd come to me for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the San Francisco\NStarley Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to reserve a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my own,\Nis that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Trowa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! So we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny we ended up\Nat the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'd be better if we\Nhelped each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Two's always better than one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Freight compartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Load yours on too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come and take over\Nthe cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I definitely won't\Nlet the mission fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How about trusting me a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He remembered my name\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this is gonna be quite\Nthe battle isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you understand\Nhow big this mission is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance to finally\Ndestroy the OZ organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This time is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna eliminate\Nevery OZ leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Then I can return to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At the New Edwards Base, United\NEarth Sphere Alliance leaders...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...including Field Marshal\NNoventa as Chief Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...General Septem, leader of\Nthe Alliance's Space Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...General Ventei, leader of the\NAlliance's Terrestrial Forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...and other top leaders\Ngather for a conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course the Specials'\NColonel Treize...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Lieutenant Colonel\NUne would also attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But Treize secretly disseminates\Nfalse information worldwide...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...stating that this meeting is\Nin fact a general meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...of top OZ officials,\Nrather than Alliance leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how the future\Nwill pan out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take whatever direction\Nyou determine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to the Alliance whether\Nmy plans to reform succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll determine the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nairobi Base is inquiring\Nabout our formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Say we're practicing\Nmaneuvers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...and conducting a simulation\Nair battle above Mombasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Noin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle might leave you\Nfeeling upset later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you, Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say this is an important\Nattack, then I'll fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance and OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if the world will\Nchange if one replaces the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So why should we even fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance was formed to\Ndeter the military powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...of nations around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But now we've become such\Na military power ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Expansion of armaments and\Nweapons development...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...wastes money and labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance shouldn't be\Nheaded in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So we should reduce the forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That would only be the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ultimate goal is for\Nunilateral demilitarization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,General Ventei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all shed blood at\None point or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't avoid it, to make\Nan ideal alliance a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But for some reason our\Nobjectives have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The time's come for us to end\Nthis period of bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we could stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But how would you deal\Nwith the recent incidents?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been under attack by\NGundanium alloy mobile suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...made in outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These indestructible suits have\Nthe Earth in a virtual crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do the Specials think;\Nyou fought with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We think the colonies made them\Nfor purely destructive purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need now is an actor\Nfrom the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,An actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone to demonstrate the\Ntrue feelings of the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural for the colonies\Nto feel uneasy toward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To rectify this, we must open\Nup dialogue with the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us begin a new chapter in\Nhistory through our discussions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't just between\Nthe colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We must also focus our\Nattention on more talks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...between the world nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But what about the problem\Nwith those mobile suits?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they understand our\Ndesire for peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...the colonies will have\Nno cause for such destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll be able to\Nfind our way once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The future's about to head\Nin the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's wait until the\Nfinal actors arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I'd like to focus on\Npeace negotiations details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Marshal! We're under attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This base is under attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This defense line isn't\Nlike the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten times more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot more than we estimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no turning\Nback now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking too long\Nto get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move in for the kill!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, the actors are all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to raise the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lieutenant Zechs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've received orders to{\i0}\N{\i1}commence Operation Daybreak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger, all units start descent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to those pilots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them we desire\Npeace with the colonies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible Marshal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The enemy's on an{\i0}\N{\i1}all-out attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could receive considerable{\i0}\N{\i1}damage wasting time talking!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Marshal, our priority should\Nbe to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't risk your getting\Nslaughtered...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...while insisting on solving\Nproblems through negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ignore your sarcasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're right, there's\Nno point getting killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if we're to promote\Npeace negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then allow me to offer you\NOZ's high speed shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready for immediate\Ntake off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have expected\Nsuch assistance from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Marshal, I'm also a member\Nof the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This way please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The shuttle is standing\Nby at gate B12!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,General Septem, this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the shuttle\Nwas that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it safer for the\Ndelegation to split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My personal shuttle is\Non standby at gate F7.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Specials' latest model,\Nbut there isn't room for many.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get as many mobile suits\Nout as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only two enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Urgent message from our\NFairbanks Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a revolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers are revolting\Nagainst the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Revolts are occurring worldwide,\None after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sergeant, it's no use!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's surrender!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you one of the\Ntraitors too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sergeant!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What can those Specials\Ndo anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This base is now under{\i0}\N{\i1}our control!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surrender at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking orders\Nfrom any rebels!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't surrender!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't overdo it,{\i0}\N{\i1}Lieutenant Noin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Creating something new\Nis wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't this a bit bloody\Nfor the laying of a foundation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Resistance is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We need as many comrades\Nas possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The era of the Alliance\Nhas ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our OZ organization must\Ngive rise to a true alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time we created\Na new system?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad if I say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This coup d'état had been\Ncarefully planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ soldiers hid their identities\Nbehind the Specials' facade...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...and were posted at each\NAlliance military base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the sabotage began\Nwithin the Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...the damage to its governing\Nbody was significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In Asia, Europe, and\Neven Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Our bases worldwide have been\Ntaken over by rebel troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So where is Marshal Noventa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! I can't\Nfind any of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! They just keep coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Missiles?! Aimed at us allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're all bunched up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No time to sit and chat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My work's cut out for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they OZ's newest models?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're attacking\Nthe Alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Those mobile suits are\Njust like ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they also be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever they are,\Nthey're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those suits are identical!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't we left yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're waiting for Marshal\NNoventa's shuttle to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an unfortunate coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't let it obstruct\Nour peace proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Marshal!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rash now, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What have they done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Marshal Noventa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for those missiles\Nearlier, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll return the favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haven't you gotten tired of{\i0}\N{\i1}these meaningless battles?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all been lured\Ninto OZ's devious trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We what?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out the Alliance's report!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys just wiped out\Nthe Alliance's pacifists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the colonies' declaration{\i0}\N{\i1}of war against us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were discussing plans for{\i0}\N{\i1}peace talks with the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Marshal Noventa was{\i0}\N{\i1}central to these plans...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and he's been assassinated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was killed by the colonies'\N{\i1}invading mobile suits!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This was a brutal invasion{\i0}\N{\i1}by the colonies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We will not yield{\i0}\N{\i1}to the colonies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We must fight them{\i0}\N{\i1}to the bitter end!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nicely done,\NGeneral Septem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be needing you\Nany further.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A magnificent performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pity you had to\Nleave the stage so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have any bloodstains\Nin Mr. Treize's wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The second act has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be getting busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all planned out by OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We became their puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Controlled by Treize\NKhushrenada's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No... how awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still gonna fight OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I've got to do it\Non my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I... What've I done?
