Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:39.10,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Watashi wo machiboukesasete nanisama no tsumori\N{\c&H00FF00&}But he makes me wait, how dare he treat me this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:43.77,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hashittekitano wakatterukedo\N{\c&H00FF00&}I know he's out of breath from running here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.04,0:22:47.20,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Sonna koto wa atari mae yo!\N{\c&H00FF00&}But that's the very least he could do for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:53.77,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Just love! Kinikuwanai aitsu\N{\c&H00FF00&}Just love! He gets on my nerves...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:23:02.51,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ijiwaru wo schichau no wa sukidakara yo\N{\c&H00FF00&}I only tease him because I actually like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.93,0:23:10.03,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Just love! Kininaru kara itsumo\N{\c&H00FF00&}Just love! I'm always thinking about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:17.47,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Murina koto itchauno chotto gomen...\N{\c&H00FF00&}Sorry I push things a little too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:21.17,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fs85.5\c&H00FF00&}Just love...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize has taken the future\Nby the reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,After being controlled\Nlike puppets...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gundams follow General\NSeptem as Lady Une's target.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, Duo, and Quatre move\Nin to prevent the explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the New Edwards Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei and Trowa head\Nstraight for Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize is cornered by\NWu Fei's sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.98,0:23:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 8,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Treize Assassination".
